step_variables._configuration_schema:
[
  {
    "title": "Source",
    "name": "source",
    "type": "select",
    "tooltip": "Retrieve the unread emails for selected folder from the Exchange server.",
    "required": false,
    "editable": true,
    "visible": true,
    "options": [
      "Inbox",
      "Sent",
      "Drafts",
      "Trash",
      "Custom Folder"
    ],
    "value": "Inbox",
    "onchange": {
      "Custom Folder": [
        {
          "title": "Folder Name",
          "tooltip": "Retrieve the unread emails from specified source folder in Exchange server",
          "name": "source_folder",
          "required": true,
          "editable": true,
          "visible": true,
          "type": "text",
          "value": ""
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "title": "Parse Inline Images",
    "name": "parse_inline",
    "type": "checkbox",
    "tooltip": "Select this option to retrieve the body of the unread emails including inline images, from the Exchange server",
    "required": false,
    "editable": true,
    "visible": true,
    "value": false
  },
  {
    "title": "Use Unified Communication",
    "name": "use_communications",
    "type": "checkbox",
    "tooltip": "Select this option to create a record of the retrieved email in the Communication Module",
    "required": false,
    "editable": true,
    "visible": true,
    "value": true
  }
]
